[SN]TITLE[SN]
Self-drive cars that go round bends and park themselves

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
The latest in self-driving car technology has been shown off at the Consumer Electronics Show in Las Vegas.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
10 January 2014 Last updated at 11:30 GMT
It includes a BMW that can snake around cones and drift round bends.
There's also a car that can find an empty parking space on its own!
